T02TD3339E:28a-1: s'i ta t'a ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD3339E:28a-3: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD3339E:28a-4: 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3339E:28a-5: ched du zla ba drug gi bar //
T02TD3339E:28a-6: sgrol ma'i 'khor lo sgom pa pos //
T02TD3339E:28b-0: 'chi ba'i skyon gyis ma gos @28b pa'i ;
T02TD3339E:28b-1: / ngag gi dbang phyug gnang byas la //
T02TD3339E:28b-2: 'chi bdag slu ba bsdus pa las //
T02TD3339E:28b-3: phyung nas sgrol ma dkar mo ni //
T02TD3339E:28b-4: bsgoms nas 'jigs pa nyams byed ma //
T02TD3339E:28b-5: bzhi pa'i sde tshan dang po aa //
T02TD3339E:28b-6: bcas las nam mkha' 'od zer spros //
T02TD3339E:28b-7: pad dkar zla ba'i gdan bltas la //
T02TD3339E:28b-8: gsum la skyabs 'gro yang brjod bya //
T02TD3339E:28b-9: rang bzhin sgro btags gzhom ched du //
T02TD3339E:28b-10: skad cig stong pa nyid du blta //
T02TD3339E:28b-11: de nas sngon gyi smon lam dbang //
T02TD3339E:28b-12: byang chub sems kyi yi ge bsgom //
T02TD3339E:28b-13: padma dkar po'i dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3339E:28b-14: zla ba'i gzugs kyi steng du ni //
T02TD3339E:28b-15: rdo rje skyil mo krung bcas pa //
T02TD3339E:28b-16: mchog sbyin pa dang autpa la 'dzin //
T02TD3339E:28b-17: ston ka'i zla ba'i 'od rnam can //
T02TD3339E:28b-18: zla ba'i rgyab la mnyam brten pa'i //
T02TD3339E:28b-19: rgyan rnams thams cad yongs su rdzogs //
T02TD3339E:28b-20: bcu drug lo lon lus can ma //
T02TD3339E:28b-21: sangs rgyas kun dang de sras kyi //
T02TD3339E:28b-23: sgrol ma de yi snying gar bsgom //
T02TD3339E:28b-25: re'u mig brgyad la yi ge brgyad //
T02TD3339E:28b-26: yongs su bskor bar bya ba'o //
T02TD3339E:28b-27: aom h'a gsal byed dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD3339E:28b-28: bsgrub bya'i ming ni lte bar bya //
T02TD3339E:28b-29: zla drug rtse gcig pa'i yid kyis //
T02TD3339E:28b-30: nges par brtan po dag tu bya //
T02TD3339E:28b-31: yi ge bcu pa'i sngags 'di ni //
T02TD3339E:28b-32: mi skyo yid kyis bzlas bya ste //
T02TD3339E:28b-33: aom gyi yi ge dang por sbyin //
T02TD3339E:28b-34: phyis ni t'a re rab tu sbyar //
T02TD3339E:28b-35: tutt'a re la tu re phyis //
T02TD3339E:28b-36: sv'a h'a mtha' ru las kun byed //
T02TD3339E:28b-37: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug zla nyi dang //
T02TD3339E:28b-38: drag po phyogs skyong 'dod lhas kyang //
T02TD3339E:28b-39: ba spu'i rtse mo 'ang gcod mi nus //
T02TD3339E:28b-40: 'chi bdag las rgyal sgrol ma bzhin //
T02TD3339E:28b-41: skra dkar gnyer ma skal ngan nad //

T02TD3339E:28b-44: sdug bsngal rab tu 'joms byed pa //
T02TD3339E:28b-45: bskul ba med par gus btud par //
T02TD3339E:28b-46: khang bzangs rin chen segs [*sogs?] kyang 'du //
T02TD3339E:28b-47: ral gri dang ni mig sman dang//
T02TD3339E:28b-48: rkang pa bum pa bzang sogs 'grub //
T02TD3339E:28b-49: tshigs bcad mkhan dang snyan ngag dang //
T02TD3339E:28b-50: blo rno shes rab dri med 'gyur //
T02TD3339E:28b-51: gzhan yang ci 'dod dngos grub ni //
T02TD3339E:28b-53: sgrol ma dkar mo'i sgrub pa'i thabs //
